							<br><div id="Detail" class="clear span-18">
<h1></h1>
<h1 style="text-align: center;">Litigation Services, Valuation<br />
and Transaction Opinions</h1>
<p>At the core of the firm’s varied advisory services is a thorough understanding of business fundamentals and the financial theory and market dynamics by which profit and opportunity translate into value. This, combined with the proven ability to communicate that knowledge in a clear, concise and compelling manner, truly differentiates Mammoth Advisors and its affiliates from their competition.</p>
<p>In litigation matters, our professionals work closely with the client’s legal team to define and clarify the issues, suggest strategies and evaluate alternatives, advise counsel regarding the substance of our analyses and those of the opposing expert, critique and rebut the opinions of opposing experts, and provide expert testimony. Because our professionals have worked and continue to work on a variety of financial and transaction advisory assignments in addition to litigation matters, their work product and testimony incorporates real-world anecdotes and insights that result in unparalleled credibility.</p>
<p>Mammoth Advisors employs focused due diligence, comprehensive research and rigorous analysis, which when coupled with extensive experience, form the underpinnings for its opinions to investors, boards of directors, senior management, creditors, regulators and triers of fact.</p>
<p>Mammoth Advisors’ professionals and affiliates have served hundreds of clients in virtually every industry, both in the United States and in foreign countries, ranging from small, closely held businesses to the Fortune 500.</p>
<p>Mammoth Advisors’ professionals and affiliates have served hundreds of clients in virtually every industry, both in the United States and in foreign countries, ranging from small, closely held businesses to the Fortune 500.  Marc Margulis, the company’s founder, has been designated as the expert witness in over 150 lawsuits, testified 75 times, performed hundreds of business valuations, and advised dozens of companies in the process of buying, selling or restructuring over his 30 year career.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><i>Contact:  Marc Margulis<br />
Office:  818-998-0092<br />
Cell:  310-922-3900</i></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
